<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 22 (KCNA) -- U.S. Defense Secretary 
William Perry's three-day visit to South Korea was a war 
monger's trip aimed at examining the war preparations against 
the North on the spot and giving a new order to the puppets. 
  During his trip, Perry held military confabs with the 
traitor 
Kim Yong-sam, the puppet defence minister and the puppet foreign 
minister and framed a series of dangerous intrigues such as 
resumption of the Team Spirit joint military maneuvers this 
year, reinforcement of U.S.-South Korea combined forces, 
strengthening of a "cooperation system" and promotion of 
"sanctions against the North" at the United Nations Security 
Council. 
  This was an unpardonable criminal act which would bring the 
situation on the Korean peninsula to a crisis and might cause a 
dangerous event. 
  Perry did not forget to cry over the "provocation" of the 
North. But this was intended to justify the aggressive design of 
the United States. 
  It goes without saying that the military provokers on the 
Korean peninsula are the United States and the South Korean 
puppet clique that deployed new-type Patriot missiles in South 
Korea and plan to extensively introduce tanks, howitzers, 
multiple rocket vehicles and other means of war. 
  The warhawk Perry's visit to South Korea and war confabs 
show 
well that the U.S. authorities have no willingness to settle the 
nuclear issue on the Korean peninsula through dialogue and 
negotiation but they are working hard to stifle the DPRK with 
strength. 
  It must not go unnoticed that the Kim Yong-sam group invited 
the U.S. defense secretary for a "close cooperation system" and 
held war confabs with him against fellow countrymen. This 
eloquently shows that the Kim Yong-sam group is a gang of 
never-to-be-condoned traitors hell-bent on war provocations 
against the North with the sinister intention to slay fellow 
countrymen in collusion with outside forces as a war servant of 
the United States. 
  Although the U.S. imperialists and the South Korean puppet 
clique are trying to strengthen the "cooperation system" and 
overpower the DPRK with strength, it is a foolish dream. 
  The U.S. imperialists and the "civilian"-veiled warmaniacs 
must refrain from rash acts, clearly mindful that their 
persistent line of war and confrontation will lead to their own 
destruction. 

</TEXT>

