BFN 

  [Text] According to a military source, the U.S. 
imperialists staged a nighttime airborne refueling exercise for 
a northward invasion on 18 and 19 April. 
  For this war exercise, two KC-130 refueling planes from an 
overseas base were deployed to a U.S. air base in South Korea in 
the afternoon of 18 April. These refueling planes, which were 
mobilized on the skies over the sea off Kunsan around 2100 hours 
