<H3> <TI>   Hosokawa Denies Role in Income Report Failure </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Hosokawa Denies Role in Income Report Failure </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   OW2204125194 Tokyo KYODO in English 1226 GMT 22 Apr 94 </F>
