of cooperation might become a real support for the Mongolian 
people such as training of Mongolian specialists, cooperation in 
the agricultural sphere especially in keeping animal husbandry 
in semideserted natural conditions, mining cultural and 
humanitarian spheres, etc. The governor general has expressed 
his gratitude for a warm welcome and hospitality during the days 
of a visit of his. 

