<F P=100> South Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Official Leaves for Russia DPRK Loggers Talks </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Official Leaves for Russia DPRK Loggers Talks </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2104031294 Seoul HANGUK ILBO in Korean 21 Apr 94 p 1 </F>
<F P=103> SK2104031294 </F>
<F P=104>  Seoul HANGUK ILBO </F>
<F P=105>  Korean </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The government urgently sent Choe Tong-chin, first 
assistant foreign minister, to Russia on 20 April to hold 
working-level discussions with the Russian Government for the 
early return of North Korean loggers to the ROK. 
  Assistant Minister Choe will meet with high-ranking 
authorities of the Russian Foreign Ministry and the Internal 
Affairs Ministry to confirm the loggers' will to defect and to 
discuss measures for their security. The ROK Foreign Ministry 
will form a working-level council headed by Assistant Minister 
Choe as soon as he returns on 23 April. 

</TEXT>

