<F P=100> South Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   XINHUA Branch Director Arrives in Seoul </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    XINHUA Branch Director Arrives in Seoul </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2204101194 Seoul YONHAP in English 0659 GMT 22 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2204101194 </F>
<F P=104>  Seoul YONHAP </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Seoul, April 22 (YONHAP) -- The director of the Hong 
Kong branch of China's XINHUA News Agency, Zhou Nan, arrived 
here Friday afternoon at the invitation of the Foreign Ministry. 
  Zhou meets with Foreign Minister Han Sung-chu later in the 
day and will call on Prime Minister Yi Hoe-chang and Trade, 
Industry and Energy Minister Kim Chol-su during his six-day stay. 
  He will also visit Samsung Electronics Co. and Daewoo Motor 
Co. as well as Songkyunkwan, a center for Confucian studies, and 
Kyongju, in North Kyongsang Province. 

</TEXT>

