<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Jakarta, April 25 KYODO -- Foreign Minister Ali 
Alatas said on Monday [25 April] that Indonesia congratulates 
Tsutomu Hata on becoming the new Japanese prime minister. 
