<H4>    Rumored Jakarta Rioting Assesed </H4>

<F P=102> BK2304085094 Jakarta Radio Republik Indonesia Network in 
Indonesian 0600 GMT 23 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2304085094 </F>
<F P=104>  Jakarta Radio Republik Indonesia Network </F>
