  [Text] A high-level Russian Foreign Ministry official 
disclosed on 22 April that Russia is exercising its influence on 
North Korea over the suspicion of the nuclear development 
through all possible political means. He added that as a part of 
its efforts, Russia invited a North Korean vice foreign minister 
to visit Moscow in the early summer. 

