<F P=102>   OW2204143994 Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME in English 1332 GMT 22 Apr 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> OW2204143994 </F>
<F P=104>  Ulaanbaatar MONTSAME </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Ulaanbaatar, April 22 (OANA-MONTSAME) -- At the 
Ministry of Trade and Industry of Mongolia there has been signed 
an agreement on establishing jointly by the ministry and the 
embassy of the USA to Mongolia of a joint fund for crediting. 
The agreement was signed by the Director General of the 
Department of Industry and Foreign Investment of the Ministry of 
Trade and Industry of Mongolia H. Ganbaatar and the Director 
General of the "Mongol Daatgal" Bank S. Goohuu. The financial 
resources of the fund worth 300 million tugrik would be assigned 
for the development of small and medium businesses, private 
sector in the five western aymags of Mongolia. 
  Present in signing ceremony of the agreement were the 
Minister of Trade and Industry T. Tsogt the Ambassador of the 
USA to Mongolia J. Johnson and other officials. 

</TEXT>

